[b]What does BoostSpeedÃ‚Â® do?[/b]

Auslogics BoostSpeed is everything you need in order to maintain and optimize your PC. This software allows you to clean and repair any damages within your system in order to make it function like you just bought it yesterday.

The Auslogics BoostSpeed comes with a long list of features:

    Cleans up your Windows registry
    Speeds up the defragmentation of your hard drive
    Makes way for more disk space
    Restores and recovers files that were accidentally deleted
    Increases the speed of your Internet connection

Every user experiences a slow computer once in a while. With this software, you are given access to functionalities such as the Disk Doctor, which helps you regain data from your previous files from a certain restore point. You are also provided with Disk Explorer, which is created in order to track down how much space your computer is currently using. Both of these tools are perfect to those who are conscious when it comes to how they are using their computers.

Overall, computers must be taken care of in order to experience its numerous benefits. With Auslogics BoostSpeed you are guaranteed a fast, reliable and, most of all, non-cluttered way of using your computer.
